{"tid":967350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「妻子愛狗勝過我」律師高樓丟2毛孩　17歲吉娃娃慘死","createTime":"2019-01-03T12:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T13:01:53.000Z","uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"66814e18f8ca021f9bb91b6b30adfdb77b20da77","tid":967350,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808790.jpg&h=ca862f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 2隻受害吉娃娃都是老狗了。（圖／取自CC0圖庫）<br />\n&nbsp;寵物小組／綜合報導<br />\n美國芝加哥51歲律師Jerald Jeske將2隻吉娃娃從高樓拋下，就因為妻子「愛狗勝過愛我」，其中17歲的吉娃娃當場死亡，14的吉娃娃仍下落不明。<br />\n這件事發生在12月24日，Jerald Jeske和妻子在車裡大吵一架，過程中賞了對方2巴掌，並大吼「你愛這些狗勝過愛我，我要把牠們殺了！」接著他跑回家用鑰匙開了門，抓了2隻吉娃娃就從陽台往下丟。其中叫做Flo的14歲吉娃娃受到驚嚇逃走，至今仍找不到，另一隻17歲吉娃娃則因為重擊死亡。<br />\nJerald Jeske因為暴行被指控虐待動物的重罪，26日以美金10000元交保，而法官下令牠不得靠近妻子和任何動物。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vygv6EQAzP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVygv6EQAzP4&d=fKH14PBUn4xEMhEcuLN8vG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a0d3b33d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vygv6EQAzP4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1347392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpets.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1347392&d=fKH14PBUn4xEMhEcuLN8vG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=747a6921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1347392</a>"},{"pid":"2dfe9e697edee0bbe5a59fa8a8d56ca16e329a2d","tid":967350,"uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.giphy.com/media/DvMHwFYLVHlZe/giphy.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FDvMHwFYLVHlZe%2Fgiphy.webp&h=49259e6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9181b046f5d12f149fc8d82ee25f250bb38fb49","tid":967350,"uid":107364,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除